items.Video_Title: Weekday Best Lunch Meal Combo | Indoor Plant Propagation | IKEA Haul | Tomato rice | Creamy Chicken
items.Video_Description:
I am an indoor plant lover and you house gets that beautiful change once you start putting hanging plats here and there. The lush green color is a beautiful site to your vision. My favourite are the pathos and I have it always with me. And few more. Have included how I grow lots from a single plant. Hope it helps. Am not an expert in gardening. Still learning from my mistakes.

Had gone to my fav store last weekend, that’s Ikea. Had some shopping there and bought few home. 

I guess rather than showing special dishes or party dishes, many of you prefer simple daily dishes. I will try to include more of such in my coming vlogs as I have been cooking everyday for my family. So sty tuned for more meal combinations. 

Take care everyone

Love you All !!
